'''Curovao ImpEx''' was an import-export business owned by the [[Curovao]] family, based on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]] in the city of [[Curovao]]. The company specialized in the transportation of military commodities and experimental technologies. The corporation was the target of many civil right activists, who claimed the corporation was exploiting natural resources on underdeveloped worlds, and crushing any opposition.

